Try it again

This is my friend Guo Jing's diary.

It records the real life experience and psychological feeling of the women who lived alone in Wuhan during the period of Fengcheng.

These words bear witness to Guo's journey from adapting to a sudden crisis to rebuilding her daily life to trying to help others.

Those who want to keep up to date can follow@guo Jing, a social worker, on Weibo.

There is Guo Jing's personal wechat qr code at the end of the article, you can also apply to add. She posts daily on her friends'network. (please don't make small talk with Guo Jing to avoid adding to her burden.)

For easy reading, this symbol will be moved centrally about every three or four days.
In the present blockade,
The property and the community are given great power,
The power to control people's lives.
20 February
Yesterday's dinner was stir-fried red cabbage and Moss with porridge.

Talking to my friends at night. People go to the park during the day, they need ID to get in. The friend expresses incomprehension. Some say it may be to keep track of someone after they've been diagnosed, but they can report it themselves. Some say it's probably just for information control. Some say it's just because they can.

Someone went to the pharmacy to buy a mask, to 13 yuan a, but the pharmacy is also very honest, wrote "very expensive, careful to buy" tips. Friends guess that the drug store may buy masks when the purchase price is very high, if the report pharmacy, it may not sell masks, people do not have to buy.

Some people go to the village checkpoints during the day on duty, want to get in and out of the people quite a lot, there are doctors, medicine, visits, and to dig herbs. The head of the village was especially careful, worried that other villages or county towns would not approve their passes, and stamped two stamps on the passes, including the village committee's and the Party's. As it turned out, the pass from another village was merely a certificate signed by the village chief.

A friend said, "there are some people who go in and out of the checkpoints without any proof. For these people, the person in charge of the checkpoints will let them in according to the actual situation. There is no certain rule about who they want to let in and out. The attitude is very important. The people who go in and out should not be too bossy or too easy to bully. " Sometimes, some rules don't have clear standards, but people do. Rule of man will lose the rules of the constraints, bullying things more likely to happen, vulnerable groups in "ask" people to do things when it is difficult to grasp what kind of attitude.

A diabolical Gif

Some people said at home to do a caramel milk tea, we have expressed envy. Friends came to interest, to demonstrate her home-made milk tea, she put sugar in the Iron Spoon First, add a little water, put the iron spoon on the stove with a small fire. Watching the sugar slowly caramelize, everyone screaming across the screen. Then, the friend uses the pan to boil the milk, puts the iron spoon directly into to stir. Milk comes out and you add black tea and you have caramel milk tea.

A friend with a sweet tooth said: "I opened Taobao, the shopping cart to fill up, looking to satisfy my appetite. "

Friends near the community some people jumped, but also some people said that the clothes fell off the floor.

When we talk about dance, some people feel that their body is not coordinated, a chance to contact modern dance, more free, began to dance modern dance. Later signed up for a modern dance class, a teacher in her dance when exaggerated to imitate her, the people around are laughing. She never went back to that dance studio.

February 20th, the neighborhood dog
(image courtesy of Guo Jing)

Today the sun is very good, looking out the window of the road, think of the open road a few days ago to try to ride a bicycle with one hand, it is so far away. I didn't learn to ride a bike until I was in college, and I used to rent a bike and ride it with my roommate in the suburbs. It was only after two years of bike sharing that I started cycling around the city, and I still get nervous when I'm in heavy traffic.

Every day there are sanitation workers to clean the area, the man put opera every day down for a walk. I had breakfast and went downstairs to get some Sun. Someone's not wearing a mask. Someone came out to walk the dog, and the dog looked around, trying to get out of its leash. The owner kept saying, "be a good boy and get some Sun. " Finally, he couldn't resist taking off the leash and letting the dog run around the yard. There are two cats in the yard, they are calling to each other.

A taxi came in and parked in front of the Property Office. Property people from the car down 20 boxes of Love Apple, and then in the group to notify everyone to the office to pick up the apple, 3 per household. I'm on my own, but I'm taking advantage. However, there are those who carry more than three apples.

On February 16th, the man who carried the apples in the neighborhood
(image courtesy of Guo Jing)

The number of people in the neighborhood grew to one hundred and twenty. These days there are five or six group purchase, only meat and eggs arrived yesterday, there are several people in the group asked: The day before yesterday ordered 50 yuan a dish order success? The property owner responded yesterday: The Community told me there was no vegetable group purchase. The vegetable package will arrive around seven o'clock today. Please pay attention to the notice. Some people asked: Around seven o'clock to which is the package AH, too many have been lost.

Some people ask: There is no need to buy eggs group? No one's responding. Someone asked the property staff: can contact staple food group purchase of rice and flour? Today launched the group purchase is 20 yuan of Cabbage Moss, I have vegetables at home, did not join.

A resident of the 2 buildings said that the kitchen drain was still leaking water. "The sewage pipe in the public area has been dredged, " said the property's staff. "The community is only responsible for this at present. The family needs to dredge it on their own. ". Another resident said the home has a pipeline, you can get the property office, 2 residents need to be able to get.

1 has the resident report: 305 room outside the platform has accumulated a lot of water, can raise fish, is the drain pipe blocked. Property says 305 is vacant. "We can't use water upstairs, " said a resident on the 5th floor of a building. "My house is flooded, and the water can't even reach it. "

A resident posted a condition in the group: a daily increase in the number of new infections (including suspected infections) for 14 days to zero is a necessary condition. Here's how:

1. The number of new infections (including suspected infections) among other people in Wuhan City was 0 per day, and the number of new infections occurred for 14 consecutive days. At the beginning of the 15th day, ready to Wu Han three towns sub-area "open. ".
2. After the conditions of 1 were met, from the 15th day, Wuhan City did not "Open" , Wuhan three towns "Open" , respectively resume the production and life study within the region, but between the three towns personnel do not exchange, traffic does not connect. If during the period of "unsealing" in the three towns, the number of new infections in the other population in Wuhan City was 0, and the data appeared continuously for 14 days, then from the 15th day, all the "unsealing" in Wuhan City would be prepared.
3. After 1 and 2 conditions are met, from the 29th day, all the inner cities of Wuhan have been "unsealed" , traffic in the city has been completely resumed, people can move freely, production, life and study in the city are in full operation. If during the period of "unsealing" , the number of new infections in other people in Wuhan City is 0 Every day, and this data appears for 14 days in a row, then from the 15th day, the city will be ready to "unseal" the outside.
4. After 1 and 2 and 3 conditions are met, from the 43rd day, Wuhan City will resume the transportation connection to the whole province, and the people in Wuhan City and the people in the whole province will move freely.

Looks like the neighborhood's GonNa be locked down for at least another two weeks.

February 19th, sunbathers in the neighborhood
(image courtesy of Guo Jing)

21 February

What is our relationship to the past? When I finished writing my diary yesterday, I stopped to have a rest, and suddenly I felt an indescribable sadness.

When people ask me where I am, I always say, "I'm better off in this situation, " and I try to remember how far away yesterday has been. Sometimes I talk about the experiences and changes of that time without any emotion, as if those things were none of my business.

It's a mechanism for trying to escape, to avoid, to protect for a while. However, we can not heal ourselves by forgetting and avoiding. I'm glad I kept a journal of how I felt during this time. I'm going to try to face it, say what I feel is the first step, and then try to understand what I'm going through and the intensity of my feelings.

The blockade has also brought collective harm and trauma, which the government must face. In this epidemic, some people have suffered unjust deaths, some patients have not received proper treatment because of the blockade, and some companies are facing bankruptcy because they can not return to work. After the outbreak, the government has to compensate some people financially, but also to remember this blockade. Only real accountability and change is responsible.

Last night's dinner was braised chicken wings with Porridge.

At meal time, the property staff informed the residents to go down to get the vegetable package. I wore a mask, did not change clothes, wearing cotton slippers downstairs. There are two sets of vegetables at the end of a line, and they are told there is only one set at the end of the line.

I didn't choose this package, and I didn't argue, so I took it and went upstairs. Set meal 50 yuan, there are winter melon, celery, chrysanthemum, lettuce, potatoes, which chrysanthemum and lettuce is particularly much, I am a bit helpless, vegetables should not be stored, it is easy to cause waste.

One of the residents came up with me, got in the elevator, and she took out a little bottle and sprayed the elevator button. I went back to my room, took off my mask, washed my hands and continued to eat.

Food served on February 20(photo courtesy of Guo Jing)

Talking to my friends at night. We're talking about the sacrifice of women. Women's pain is often overlooked. Women are taken for granted when they have to sacrifice for their families and children. Women are discouraged from using anesthesia during childbirth, often on the grounds that it is not good for the baby, and some say other women can tolerate it.

Some people refer to Mulan's dilemma, in which a woman has to work like a man, to compete, to have a career, to come home and be a wife and mother. However, women in the workplace is difficult to get equal opportunities, in the family pay can not be recognized in practice.

When we talk about nurses getting their hair cut and why hair is so important to women, cutting nails doesn't make women feel so strongly about it.

Friends who once shaved their heads to protest gender inequality in college admissions have shared their experience that in a patriarchal society, looks are part of the social fabric. Women who shave their heads are seen as the exception, it's hard to interview for a job, it's socially isolated, and we rarely see a bald woman in a formal setting.

In addition, hair also has the effect of heat preservation, bald will be easy to catch a cold, hair growth process will also have discomfort. Therefore, when we explain the structure, we must also take into account the actual rules of the barriers to women.

Mulan in makeup

A friend said the neighbors beat and scolded the children every day. She wrote a letter to her neighbor, saying:
"please don't hit the children any more. Otherwise, it is the responsibility of those who know to call the police to stop you from committing domestic violence, because domestic violence is illegal. Article thirty-three of the Law of the People's Republic of China on combating domestic violence stipulates: If the perpetrator commits domestic violence, which constitutes an act against the administration of Public Security, he shall be punished according to law for the Administration of Public Security; if the act constitutes a crime, he shall be investigated for criminal responsibility according to law. It is not easy to educate children, but please stick to the equal, respectful and legal way. Call 110 or 12338 if you experience or hear abuse! Peace and health to your family!"

She slipped the letter under the door into the neighbor's house.

In the chat, the bathroom door above the door shaft suddenly broken, the door fell half. I couldn't laugh or cry, so I just kept it open.

I had a dream that I was trapped in a room with people arguing outside the door, and I couldn't do anything.

It's very dark today. It should rain tonight. The ground is wet. I woke up at 8 am, exhausted and exhausted. The man with the opera was walking downstairs.

I kept to my daily routine, exercising, eating breakfast, and then doing a bit of work.

Wu Han's life was narrowed down to a wechat group.

Property staff issued a 20 kg of rice group purchase, said: Special Times our self-government group comrades are very hard, rice order this time, I hope you have enough food (preliminary isolation until March 10) . Everyone has joined the group purchase.

Someone from the other group to see the fruit of the group, sent to ask: Who Spell Fruit? Then in the group put together a group to buy fruit, 30 from send, the group is not a lot of people, launched the group is very worried, said: do not eat, how to waste time. Someone asked, do you have any Tahini sauce? No one answered him.

A few residents of building 1 went to the Property Office in the morning to discuss the problem of sewer water. In the afternoon, finally had the good news, was originally the third floor Corner Block, temporarily opened the pipe a hole. The flooded residents can finally breathe a sigh of relief.

After lunch, I slept for two hours. I got up feeling dizzy. The property group informed everyone to go down to get rice and free cabbage. I went downstairs to get some food. Sit Down to write a diary, but my head is too ignorant to think, in the room back and forth for a while, only gradually sober some.

22 February

People who live under the covers now have to rely on group buying. At first, it was only available through community groups. However, people's life is too depressed, can not only meet the group purchase survival needs of food, but also some unreasonable group purchase with dissatisfaction. Everyone has their own group purchase. Everyone in the other community to see the group purchase on their own community.

There are always people who have connections. A man in my neighborhood once organized people to buy fruit in a group. Today, it was like a magic trick. He grabbed six bags of salt, six bottles of Vinegar, six boxes of Yogurt, and got a lot of eggs. He asked if anyone wanted them, four Yuan for salt, seven yuan for Vinegar, 50 Yuan for Yogurt, 30 yuan for 25 eggs.

A friend sent me a video of a resident in a neighborhood group accusing the neighborhood of inaction and Loot a burning house. She pointed out that many times in the community residents are self-help, alcohol and masks is the Industry Committee to buy, property disinfection materials are donated by the owners.

Someone said, "the community has a limited number of people. " She asked what the community had done? The community now takes over the work of the Industry Committee directly, and just gives out a queue. She added, "The supermarket package is ridiculous. Buy Rice with papyrus and soy sauce. "

Last night's dinner was stir-fried pork with celery and porridge.

Talking to my friends at night. Some people dance during the day, some people work, some people help their families take care of their children, some people watch movies. Some people in the county removed the checkpoint, the county can be free movement.

We talked about the confirmed cases in many prisons, 230 cases in women's prison and 207 cases in Rencheng District prison. The number of people who have been infected is so large that we can see it in the media. Can patients in prison be treated? Prison population mobility has been relatively small, and the situation in the detention center? There are many densely populated places, such as nursing homes, welfare homes, and these places of prevention and control measures?

When chatting, a friend suddenly told me: "You cough a little too much today. " I did not notice, that my hypochondria is not so serious, not constantly worried about their own symptoms of illness. In fact, hypochondria has always been with me, occasionally cough much, I bubble a vitamin C effervescent tablets to drink, as a placebo.

Fog outside the window on February 22
(image courtesy of Guo Jing)

Wake up at 8:00 in the morning, sleepy eyes open the window, smoke outside. Just in the morning someone in the community group to cover the sweat some place fire video, I was shocked. I put on my glasses to make sure it was just fog.

It was after 10:00, and the sun cleared the fog, so I went downstairs to get some Sun.

Someone was wearing two masks, probably because yesterday someone in the group sent a message saying there was a suspected case in another neighborhood. Someone saw it and said, "the group buying group is having a great time, just like the festival, the express delivery has received Super Hi, now it's OK, the previous period of closure was all in vain! " I don't know if this suspected case was actually infected by the group buying, and the groupon takes the fall.

My residential property in the group sent a message: I suggest that everyone, if there is a basic material security, do not find a person again this group that, during the outbreak of life is important. The next building, more risk! Patience will soon pass, if the contact of people messy, then the whole community or even cover sweat to pay a greater price! However, many people buy group because they are not sure when the blockade will pass, want their current life better.

I'm an outsider in this neighborhood, and I don't know any other residents. A lot of the residents are local people, they said to cover sweat, some people are chatting, I want to eavesdrop can not eavesdrop.

A car came back from outside, and it looked like someone from the neighborhood was driving it, and I don't know how they got in or out. From the trunk of the residents took out two or three bags, bags containing mainly snacks, melon seeds, barbecue, and so on.

Community today to the group purchase is flour and hot dry noodles, in view of the flour at home I have not used, did not buy new. Others are happy to bask in their own hot-and-dry noodles and Eggnog. Today the community group began to buy sesame paste, more than a dozen people have joined the group purchase. Looks like the sweats really love Tahini.

Today, a family of three went downstairs to the sun, the boy about ten years old, took a jump rope, jump in the yard, a while his mother also jumped with him. The boy danced for a while, said, "it's too hot, " and took off his coat.

When he was tired of dancing, he played games with his mother, first clapping his hands, and then playing the game of the Crutch (a game in which one leg is independent, the other leg is bent forward, and the hands or one-handed grip of the feet make the knees pop forward and attack the other with one knee) . He was very happy. Father has been standing around watching, in the mother and son play the time when the judge, said to the boy: "How can you use the hand? " I looked at the side can not help but happy. They play tired, go to the property to take home a group purchase, I also went upstairs.

February 22nd, residents playing in the neighborhood

23 February

People who make demands are easily taken as troublemakers, even if they are reasonable demands.

The situation of each household in the community is different. When I reported my body temperature the other morning, I saw that there were five or six people in some families. Sealed a week, some households in the home should eat the food is almost. Yesterday someone in the group asked: "The property is not organized group purchase now? Need to call their own errands to buy food? "

Property people asked: "Our Autonomous Office just organized a group purchase of meat, eggs, vegetables, and yesterday issued a Chinese cabbage, you have finished? " Then several people said: now the property can only maintain a normal life procurement! I think property management is very good! In a flash, the person who made the request became a troublemaker, she said helplessly: "No one said the property is not good, Chinese culture is broad and profound, do not misinterpret the meaning. "

Another property owner said, "If everyone participates in the group purchase, there should be no problem in the last half month. " Others pointed out the risks of group purchase, some people retorted: "That property group purchase is not infected. " At the beginning of the question said: "I entered the group on the 18th, the Group Organization group purchase I have participated, have been waiting for delivery, has not been news, everyone is not malicious. It's just that everyone is in a different position, from a different angle, and it's normal to think differently."

The person who asked the question just spoke out of their normal needs, inexplicably someone to maintain the property, there was a conflict. At this time I am also very weak, I dare not easily and others conflict, during the blockade I can only rely on this group, rely on the people who organize group buying property.

I think of Stockholm Syndrome, when the victim's life is completely in the control of the perpetrator, the victim has no chance to escape, the victim will rely on the perpetrator, and the perpetrators of small favors to express gratitude, and even to defend the perpetrators.

It's a survival mechanism for the powerless in the face of power. I do not say that a property is a "perpetrator" , but at the moment of the blockade, property, the community has been given a great power, this power can control people's survival.

Last night's dinner was mushroom and pork with Rice gruel.

Talking to my friends at night. Some went to the supermarket for the first time after the blockade, bought snacks, others went out to play, had their temperature taken many times, and had seafood and beef hotpot.

We talked about some tragedies in the epidemic situation. Tong's car was used to block the road because of the epidemic situation in Tong Wo Wan, Wangji Street, Xinzhou district, Wuhan. On the 20th, the captain wanted to send someone out, so he went to Tong's home and asked him to move the car. Tong refused. Captain and a quarrel up, a wife and daughter out of a quarrel, the captain took a knife stabbed a child, three people died.

The cause of the incident reported by the Xinzhou Public Security Bureau was a dispute between neighbors. During the outbreak, the fear of pneumonia, the anxiety of being forced to stay at home, and the uncertainty of despair about the future, all of which would have led to violence if they had not been relieved.

The parents of a couple who left their newborn baby at the People's overseas Chinese hospital in the city of Chenghai, Shantou, left a note saying that they had used up all their savings after giving birth and that their pneumonia was so severe that they had no income, hope the hospital or the police station to send the child to the welfare home, they go to find a job, if survive, must go to the welfare home within a month to pick up the child, then also give the welfare home maintenance.

Someone commented, didn't you think you could raise him properly before you died? But the poor also have the right to have children, and no one is more qualified to have children than others.

How on earth can we prevent more tragedies? The government needs to evaluate prevention and control measures and try to take into account the situation of different people as well as the emotional impact of the blockade.

February 23rd, the neighborhood
(image courtesy of Guo Jing)

We talked about the "100 things you have to do in life" recently spread in the circle of friends, such as "owning your own house" and "punching cards in Chinese provinces and cities" . This list is uncomfortable, it's a reflection of the social appraisal system, implicit in the social comparison. The more things you do, the more you feel superior.

But some of the things that some people are destined to be unable to do, and they can not do it not for personal reasons, but the lack of social resources. There's not much to do in life, just do your best. One Netizen said at the beginning of the blockade: to This Day, relying on your Iq, contacts, financial resources, have you got to buy a mask? If you don't get it, don't think about special medicine.

Yesterday many people in the community group in the other community in the case of new cases. Now can not out of the community, so rare and contact with others is to get the group purchase of food, we are all nervous. Organize everyone to buy fruit is more worried, she told to take fruit of the residents mask, gloves, disinfectant, etc. , she was afraid of accidents.

We also talk about scattered downstairs to get fruit, a down to 3 people, in the group call. ! She also worried about using alcohol inappropriate fire, in the group sent three times: You disinfection, use alcohol, do not fire! ÔºÅ! !

The driver delivered too much yesterday, so he changed it to today. And the delivery guy said there was traffic control and no delivery today. Some people said: "The traffic control will be more strict tomorrow. " Several people said: If the fruit can't arrive today, forget it! Therefore, the Organization of the group purchase of the people on the money one by one returned to the residents.

The other liked to walk around and talk to each other occasionally. I don't know how they got out of the house, maybe their neighborhood was abandoned, maybe they were construction workers stuck here, didn't belong to any community. They're outside the wall. Someone's walking the dog.

Generally brush to 10 o'clock can pay. "

21 February

What is our relationship to the past? When I finished writing my diary yesterday, I stopped to have a rest, and suddenly I felt an indescribable sadness.

When people ask me where I am, I always say, "I'm better off in this situation, " and I try to remember how far away yesterday has been. Sometimes I talk about the experiences and changes of that time without any emotion, as if those things were none of my business.

It's a mechanism for trying to escape, to avoid, to protect for a while. However, we can not heal ourselves by forgetting and avoiding. I'm glad I kept a journal of how I felt during this time. I'm going to try to face it, say what I feel is the first step, and then try to understand what I'm going through and the intensity of my feelings.

The blockade has also brought collective harm and trauma, which the government must face. In this epidemic, some people have suffered unjust deaths, some patients have not received proper treatment because of the blockade, and some companies are facing bankruptcy because they can not return to work. After the outbreak, the government has to compensate some people financially, but also to remember this blockade. Only real accountability and change is responsible.

Talking to my friends at night. We're talking about the sacrifice of women. Women's pain is often overlooked. Women are taken for granted when they have to sacrifice for their families and children. Women are discouraged from using anesthesia during childbirth, often on the grounds that it is not good for the baby, and some say other women can tolerate it.

Some people refer to Mulan's dilemma, in which a woman has to work like a man, to compete, to have a career, to come home and be a wife and mother. However, women in the workplace is difficult to get equal opportunities, in the family pay can not be recognized in practice.

When we talk about nurses getting their hair cut and why hair is so important to women, cutting nails doesn't make women feel so strongly about it.

Friends who once shaved their heads to protest gender inequality in college admissions have shared their experience that in a patriarchal society, looks are part of the social fabric. Women who shave their heads are seen as the exception, it's hard to interview for a job, it's socially isolated, and we rarely see a bald woman in a formal setting.

In addition, hair also has the effect of heat preservation, bald will be easy to catch a cold, hair growth process will also have discomfort. Therefore, when we explain the structure, we must also take into account the actual rules of the barriers to women.

Today, a family of three went downstairs to the sun, the boy about ten years old, took a jump rope, jump in the yard, a while his mother also jumped with him. The boy danced for a while, said, "it's too hot, " and took off his coat.

When he was tired of dancing, he played games with his mother, first clapping his hands, and then playing the game of the Crutch (a game in which one leg is independent, the other leg is bent forward, and the hands or one-handed grip of the feet make the knees pop forward and attack the other with one knee) . He was very happy. Father has been standing around watching, in the mother and son play the time when the judge, said to the boy: "How can you use the hand? " I looked at the side can not help but happy. They play tired, go to the property to take home a group purchase, I also went upstairs.

February 22nd, residents playing in the neighborhood

23 February

People who make demands are easily taken as troublemakers, even if they are reasonable demands.

The situation of each household in the community is different. When I reported my body temperature the other morning, I saw that there were five or six people in some families. Sealed a week, some households in the home should eat the food is almost. Yesterday someone in the group asked: "The property is not organized group purchase now? Need to call their own errands to buy food? "

Property people asked: "Our Autonomous Office just organized a group purchase of meat, eggs, vegetables, and yesterday issued a Chinese cabbage, you have finished? " Then several people said: now the property can only maintain a normal life procurement! I think property management is very good! In a flash, the person who made the request became a troublemaker, she said helplessly: "No one said the property is not good, Chinese culture is broad and profound, do not misinterpret the meaning. "

Another property owner said, "If everyone participates in the group purchase, there should be no problem in the last half month. " Others pointed out the risks of group purchase, some people retorted: "That property group purchase is not infected. " At the beginning of the question said: "I entered the group on the 18th, the Group Organization group purchase I have participated, have been waiting for delivery, has not been news, everyone is not malicious. It's just that everyone is in a different position, from a different angle, and it's normal to think differently."

The person who asked the question just spoke out of their normal needs, inexplicably someone to maintain the property, there was a conflict. At this time I am also very weak, I dare not easily and others conflict, during the blockade I can only rely on this group, rely on the people who organize group buying property.

I think of Stockholm Syndrome, when the victim's life is completely in the control of the perpetrator, the victim has no chance to escape, the victim will rely on the perpetrator, and the perpetrators of small favors to express gratitude, and even to defend the perpetrators.

It's a survival mechanism for the powerless in the face of power. I do not say that a property is a "perpetrator" , but at the moment of the blockade, property, the community has been given a great power, this power can control people's survival.

Last night's dinner was mushroom and pork with Rice gruel.

Talking to my friends at night. Some went to the supermarket for the first time after the blockade, bought snacks, others went out to play, had their temperature taken many times, and had seafood and beef hotpot.

We talked about some tragedies in the epidemic situation. Tong's car was used to block the road because of the epidemic situation in Tong Wo Wan, Wangji Street, Xinzhou district, Wuhan. On the 20th, the captain wanted to send someone out, so he went to Tong's home and asked him to move the car. Tong refused. Captain and a quarrel up, a wife and daughter out of a quarrel, the captain took a knife stabbed a child, three people died.

The cause of the incident reported by the Xinzhou Public Security Bureau was a dispute between neighbors. During the outbreak, the fear of pneumonia, the anxiety of being forced to stay at home, and the uncertainty of despair about the future, all of which would have led to violence if they had not been relieved.

The parents of a couple who left their newborn baby at the People's overseas Chinese hospital in the city of Chenghai, Shantou, left a note saying that they had used up all their savings after giving birth and that their pneumonia was so severe that they had no income, hope the hospital or the police station to send the child to the welfare home, they go to find a job, if survive, must go to the welfare home within a month to pick up the child, then also give the welfare home maintenance.

Someone commented, didn't you think you could raise him properly before you died? But the poor also have the right to have children, and no one is more qualified to have children than others.

How on earth can we prevent more tragedies? The government needs to evaluate prevention and control measures and try to take into account the situation of different people as well as the emotional impact of the blockade.

February 23rd, the neighborhood

We talked about the "100 things you have to do in life" recently spread in the circle of friends, such as "owning your own house" and "punching cards in Chinese provinces and cities" . This list is uncomfortable, it's a reflection of the social appraisal system, implicit in the social comparison. The more things you do, the more you feel superior.

But some of the things that some people are destined to be unable to do, and they can not do it not for personal reasons, but the lack of social resources. There's not much to do in life, just do your best. One Netizen said at the beginning of the blockade: to This Day, relying on your Iq, contacts, financial resources, have you got to buy a mask? If you don't get it, don't think about special medicine.
